OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine. The
OL,7,Frest of the night will be generally
OL,8,Fdry with clear periods and the odd
OL,9,Fpassing shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FMainly dry with some sunny
OL,12,Fspells, but there will be a scattering
OL,13,Fof showers across the west.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,16,FSunday and Monday with some warm
OL,17,Fspells of sunshine. Patchy rain on
OL,18,FTuesday, mainly in the west.
